### ============================================
### USERS (via Gateway - necessite JWT)
### ============================================

### Get all users
# Remplacer <TOKEN> par le accessToken recu du login
GET http://localhost:3000/users
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Get user by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/users/<USER_ID>
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### Create user
POST http://localhost:3000/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

{
    "email": "test.user@immo360.com",
    "firstName": "Test",
    "lastName": "User",
    "role": "OCCUPANT"
}

### Update user
PATCH http://localhost:3000/users/<USER_ID>
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

{
    "firstName": "Updated",
    "lastName": "Name"
}

### Delete user
DELETE http://localhost:3000/users/<USER_ID>
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>

### ============================================
### SYNC SERVICE - HISTORY
### ============================================

### Get operation history
GET http://localhost:3003/history

### Get history with filters
GET http://localhost:3003/history?status=SUCCESS&limit=10

### Get stats
GET http://localhost:3003/history/stats

### Get entity history
GET http://localhost:3003/history/entity/<USER_ID>

